\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7828a49f0ffda0f2fed39d689f7ccfd12b85536f","tid":2032102,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"荷蘭球星雲佩斯在個人的書中評論了三位主教練：費格遜、雲高爾和雲格。<br />\n<br />\n  雲佩斯在英超時效力過阿仙奴和曼聯，在荷蘭國家隊與雲高爾共事。他寫道：「費格遜真的是一個超級主教練。」<br />\n<br />\n  「雲格是費格遜和雲高爾的結合，他總是強調所有積極的方面，他會考慮什麼是有效的，並想的很長遠。」<br />\n<br />\n  「戰術上說，雲高爾是一個天才，這是你無法否認的。」"},{"pid":"4f8478b78405b55d20d2e5b922d2e586b68eed21","tid":2032102,"uid":28202,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雲加像是費格遜和雲高爾的結合體</span></span>"},{"pid":"031df32c03c488e14d12fef17151d01eb241ea18","tid":2032102,"uid":205719,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"無雲加荷甲執你返黎<br />\n年年玻璃都等你<br />\n你做撚到球星咩"},{"pid":"adcbbedcd4132e3ef658fbc8b58abfb257192468","tid":2032102,"uid":164730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"031df32c03c488e14d12fef17151d01eb241ea18","tid":2032102,"uid":205719,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"無雲加荷甲執你返黎<br />\n年年玻璃都等你<br />\n你做撚到球星咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:01:05.000Z","msg":"25仔，唔識感恩"},{"pid":"f07ed9adcd03993b3516268c23610c4f94e69be9","tid":2032102,"uid":103235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"費sir同隊波宣佈退休時第一件事係向雲佩斯同香川道歉"},{"pid":"1888d72a91ab36b7028e06032bddadc3bff54e4c","tid":2032102,"uid":324041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"冇計啦！果陣阿仙奴要起新球場，搞到要年年賣自己隊長當家球星保命先掂!咁都keep住有前四打歐聯，雲加好叻叻㗎啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbad0fc98f2cdbc3f72f017f18b1ce980080f66b","tid":2032102,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":